SUMMARY:The Vampire Run
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:A dark and stormy night. A vampire’s castle outlined by light
 ning. An hour to find and kill the dreaded fiend... And one idiot trying to
  manage the escalating chaos. Join a fast-paced\, hilariously deadly choose
 -your-own adventure! Three players at a time must decide how to approach a 
 variety of fiendish obstacles to reach the vampire’s chamber\, BUT one of
  the players is evil and the audience must decide who before it’s too lat
 e. This is the debut solo show from award winning writer and performer Jona
 than Laury (Best Comedy\, Unrestricted View Film Festival 2019). Think some
 thing like Knightmare meets Traitors\, hosted by the lovechild of Vincent P
 rice and Alex Horne... Shortlisted for the Glitch award at the Lambeth Frin
 ge\, and described by audiences as 'Brilliant\, slick\, funny\, 10/10 would
  go again' and 'My favourite theatrical experience of 2025.' It’s a comed
 y\, it’s a horror\, it’s a game\, it’s a show! And it’s definitely 
 the most fun you can have dying horribly.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.a
 pp/comedy-atlas/event/the-vampire-run-5855/
URL:https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/the-vampire-run-5855/
END:VEVENT
